### 1. 测试获取酒店列表
GET http://localhost:3000/api/hotels/gethotellist?userId=&keyword=&location=&stars=&score=&priceRange=&tags=[1]&asParking=true

### 2. 测试查询详情 
GET http://localhost:3000/api/hotels/gethotelinfo?hotelId={{testHotelId}}

### 3. 测试添加/修改酒店基本信息 (PUT)
### 情况 A: 修改已有酒店的基本信息
PUT http://localhost:3000/api/hotels/creathotelinfo
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "userId": 2,
    "hoteliId": "{{testHotelId}}",
    "hotelName": "宜宿大酒店 (旗舰店)",
    "hotelierName": "张经理",
    "hoteliEmail": "zhang@yisuo.com",
    "hoteliAddress": "上海市浦东新区陆家嘴金融中心 88 号"
}
### 情况 B: 新增酒店基本信息 (不带 ID)
PUT http://localhost:3000/api/hotels/creathotelinfo
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "userId": 2,
    "hotelName": "新宜宿酒店",
    "hotelierName": "王经理",
    "hoteliEmail": "wang@yisuo.com",
    "hoteliAddress": "北京市朝阳区三里屯路 1 号"
}
### 情况 C: 管理员修改已有酒店的基本信息
PUT http://localhost:3000/api/hotels/creathotelinfo
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "userId": 1,
    "status": 1,
    "score": 4.5,
    "hoteliId": "{{testHotelId}}"
}
